analysis.description:
RecoverCurrency.recoverEther (/unique_chucks/11/0xe92065d8bb2392121a8fbe6a81e79782fbc89dd4.sol#248-251) sends eth to arbitrary user
	Dangerous calls:
	- msg.sender.transfer(address(this).balance) (/unique_chucks/11/0xe92065d8bb2392121a8fbe6a81e79782fbc89dd4.sol#250)

TokenLedger.totalsupply (/unique_chucks/11/0xe92065d8bb2392121a8fbe6a81e79782fbc89dd4.sol#385-386) is never initialized. It is used in:
	- totalSupply (/unique_chucks/11/0xe92065d8bb2392121a8fbe6a81e79782fbc89dd4.sol#534-537)

RecoverCurrency.recoverToken (/unique_chucks/11/0xe92065d8bb2392121a8fbe6a81e79782fbc89dd4.sol#254-264) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-token.transfer(msg.sender,balance) (/unique_chucks/11/0xe92065d8bb2392121a8fbe6a81e79782fbc89dd4.sol#264)

IntimateShoppe.backTokenOwner (/unique_chucks/11/0xe92065d8bb2392121a8fbe6a81e79782fbc89dd4.sol#939-953) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-token.freezeAccount(msg.sender) (/unique_chucks/11/0xe92065d8bb2392121a8fbe6a81e79782fbc89dd4.sol)

Reentrancy in IntimateShoppe.backTokenOwner (/unique_chucks/11/0xe92065d8bb2392121a8fbe6a81e79782fbc89dd4.sol#939-953):
	External calls:
	- token.transferFrom(wallet_address,msg.sender,tokens) (/unique_chucks/11/0xe92065d8bb2392121a8fbe6a81e79782fbc89dd4.sol)
	- token.freezeAccount(msg.sender) (/unique_chucks/11/0xe92065d8bb2392121a8fbe6a81e79782fbc89dd4.sol)
	External calls sending eth:
	- wallet_address.transfer(address(this).balance) (/unique_chucks/11/0xe92065d8bb2392121a8fbe6a81e79782fbc89dd4.sol#949)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- tokensSold (/unique_chucks/11/0xe92065d8bb2392121a8fbe6a81e79782fbc89dd4.sol)
	- weiRaised (/unique_chucks/11/0xe92065d8bb2392121a8fbe6a81e79782fbc89dd4.sol)
